name: Minty Blue/Green Flower Post Earrings
description:
Bead woven and fabricated sterling silver loopy flower earrings. Materials include French glass seed beads, tiny sterling tube beads, sterling silver, and colored thread. Silver is oxidised.

These are post earrings, and are very lightweight.

Size is 1 1/4" diameter at the widest point.

Shipped insured.

name: Daytime Stars Ring
description:
A slightly concave sterling silver disc displays tiny dots of faceted fine silver. Some dots also show off tiny opaline aquamarine vintage Italian glass seed beads, which look like stars would look in a blue day light sky.

This is a sturdy ring constructed of sterling silver, except the little faceted dots, which are fine siver. Disc measures 1 inch.

This ring is made to order. Just let me know what size you need, and I will make it special for you. This will take 10-14 days.

name: Poppy Red Tulip Earrings (short)
description:
A shorter version of my tulip earrings, these are made of sterling silver, copper, and pigmented epoxy resin. A tulip shape is sawed from copper sheet, formed, and painted with 4 layers of pigmented epoxy resin. This is soldered to a sterling silver "stem" with individually balled sterling silver wire. Oxidized and finished with sandpaper.

Length is 2 inches.

name: Pink Whitehearts Stacking Rings (set of 6)
description:
Little vintage pink whiteheart glass beads are featured on a thin hammered sterling silver band along with a small silver faceted dot. Pink whitehearts are no longer being made and are very beautiful and rare. Very subtle brushed finish on silver.

This listing is for a set of 6 rings.

These are made to order...please contact me to let me know what size you need.
